{"remainingRequest":"/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/node_modules/vue-loader/lib/index.js??ref--1-1!/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/node_modules/vuepress/lib/webpack/markdownLoader.js??ref--1-2!/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/adaptation/accessibility/perceivable/easy-to-know/use-of-color.md?vue&type=template&id=50590d05&","dependencies":[{"path":"/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/adaptation/accessibility/perceivable/easy-to-know/use-of-color.md","mtime":1540958169746},{"path":"/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/node_modules/cache-loader/dist/cjs.js","mtime":499162500000},{"path":"/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/node_modules/vue-loader/lib/loaders/templateLoader.js","mtime":499162500000},{"path":"/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/node_modules/cache-loader/dist/cjs.js","mtime":499162500000},{"path":"/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/node_modules/vue-loader/lib/index.js","mtime":499162500000},{"path":"/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/node_modules/vuepress/lib/webpack/markdownLoader.js","mtime":1533872387000}],"contextDependencies":[],"result":["\n<div class=\"content\"><h1 id=\"合理使用颜色\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#合理使用颜色\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a> 合理使用颜色</h1>\n<h2 id=\"描述\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#描述\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a> 描述</h2>\n<p>颜色并不是用来传达信息的唯一视觉方式，确保通过颜色区分之后达到的视觉效果也可以通过文本来实现。\n如果仅仅通过颜色差异来传达信息，那么对于色盲或者色弱这类有颜色区分障碍的用户将很难从中获取到信息，因此需要提供另外一种视觉方式来提供信息，确保看不到颜色的用户也能获取到信息。</p>\n<h2 id=\"例子\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#例子\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a> 例子</h2>\n<h3 id=\"bad-case\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#bad-case\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a> bad case</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>百度口碑商家注册，当有必填项未填时，仅仅通过颜色来提示用户，对看不到颜色的用户不友好</p>\n  <img src=\"https://agroup-bos.su.bcebos.com/0a3c851f5b751563b56fbc4a4fb7e7b56ccb17cf\" alt=\"百度口碑商家注册\" width=\"250\">\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"指导建议\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#指导建议\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a> 指导建议</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>使用颜色加文本的方式呈现信息，而不是纯颜色</li>\n<li>为带颜色标识的控件提供文本标注</li>\n<li>当使用颜色差异去传递不同信息时，确保搭配其它视觉提示</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"相关文档\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#相关文档\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a> 相关文档</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/UNDERSTANDING-WCAG20/visual-audio-contrast-without-color.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">W3C Use of Color<OutboundLink/></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n",null]}